Want to know how to make a hair mask at home for smoother and shiner hair?

All you need is - Rice Flour, Honey, Aloe Vera and Ghee
Mix it all well and apply it through the lengths of your hair, leave it for an hour and wash off which a shampoo followed by conditioner.

You can use the same mask for your face as well but if you are someone with an acne prone skin avoid it on the face.

#hairmask #diyhairmask #hairmaskathome #healthyhair #shinyhair #hair #smoothhair #silklyhair
